{"tid":298515,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「比鬼責」睡眠癱瘓症集中討論區","createTime":"2017-06-26T10:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T19:46:03.000Z","uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63307fd5113c86e0dafef748c1ecc0541e125715","tid":298515,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:53:25.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想知各位巴c經歷同埋咩原因令你有and你點解決"},{"pid":"92e8c5f91957e34be908152764d060d931295685","tid":298515,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:55:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">睡眠癱瘓症通常發生在人類剛進入睡眠或將醒未醒時。患者感覺自己剛剛醒過來，可以睜開雙眼並看到周圍事物的影像以及聽到周圍的聲音，但是無法移動軀幹和四肢，也無法發出聲音，有時會產生幻覺並看到虛擬的影像，嚴重的病例會感到呼吸困難。  <br />\n<br />\n睡眠癱瘓常伴有恐慌發作，因為人還處於有意識的狀態。同時伴隨聽覺和視覺上的幻覺，對於睡眠癱瘓也是很典型的，然後漸漸進入「夢境」。<br />\n<br />\n通常還會有「假醒」，即人醒過來，發現自己原來還在夢裏，現實中也還在睡眠。這樣的「假醒」通常會多次重複，伴隨的還有來自於對這種無終止重複的恐懼。通常是可以打斷這種重複與麻痹的，如通過試着對小指的移動等。<br />\n<br />\n睡眠癱瘓經常會有呼吸困難與耳裏的聲響的感覺，經常被誤認為血液循環問題。很多人有過一次睡眠癱瘓的經歷，有些人卻會經常發生。睡眠癱瘓也可能是發作性嗜睡病或心律不整的症狀。還可能是癲癇、偏頭痛、焦慮障礙、阻塞性睡眠呼吸暫停等的表現。</span>"},{"pid":"c60c7da129425ffaef799885ea6f7dc1319f6fe2","tid":298515,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">另有狀況是已經睡醒，意識清楚，但全身難以動彈，眼睜不開，亦或不敢睜開，通常伴隨者恐怖式的幻聽，本身也有睜眼定會看到恐怖情境的直覺。<br />\n<br />\n強行清醒：自身是可以強制動彈與睜眼，只是上述之情況在過程中會更加強烈，一旦睜眼後，所有症狀瞬時消失。<br />\n<br />\n此類症狀在數分鐘後會自然消失，患者身體逐漸恢復動作，根據絕大多數的案例研究，睡眠癱瘓症對身體無害，但對部分有此體驗者的精神與經濟算是有害，因部分體驗者容易與鬼怪作為聯想，也容易被勸服相信是如此，從而尋求民間命館、神明、廟宇等諸如此類，進而供奉大小額不等的金錢，而不尋求醫學上建議，電視靈異節目所謂鬼壓床等靈異事件也大多出至於此。</span>"},{"pid":"ca5dafbcb9409a206daf50d0ad82f3dc3980618d","tid":298515,"uid":61201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:56:32.000Z","msg":"考dse果期試過一日4,5次"},{"pid":"97ce6b00ad397e7039f1bf425f36e93a2d451359","tid":298515,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:57:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://health.ettoday.net/news/802538\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhealth.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F802538&d=kflC9PVWCPKvjn1plzwuSbr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=1391b04e\" target=\"_blank\">http://health.ettoday.net/news/802538</a><br />\n鬼壓床其實是一種病！睡眠癱瘓症通常發生在2個時間點"},{"pid":"b5783145d555ee7731f1b748ebf62107ee3020e9","tid":298515,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:58:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>考dse果期試過一日4,5次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nme2 <br />\n晏就會無啦啦好晏訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34254e76f80b687702c86118fab4c0c60f96e443","tid":298515,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好辛苦..."},{"pid":"0755192cf366c232f0dc6f36f43e2abef69a30fc","tid":298515,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:02:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c7630ec66a3af57826b0f2b6b2348a443b2027d","tid":298515,"uid":59466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:05:31.000Z","msg":"我以前係面向天會成日有事，打側就好d<br />\n<br />\n而家已經少左好多，冇咩事，但冇特別做d咩"},{"pid":"964ad26aca80bc6794d7fba964c50ad8d1d8c6cf","tid":298515,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:09:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過訓訓下半夜感覺到係咁有野想扯你落床, 而我就下意識咁捉實張被同佢鬥扯<br />\n但係成個人麻痹哂起唔到身又嗌唔到<br />\n果下真係覺得好無助好恐怖<br />\n因為個人係清醒但個身就郁唔到<br />\n一直到天光先無事<br />\n試過好幾次呢種情況<br />\n之後安返個神位係屋就再無試過了</blockquote><br />\n 真係有野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我係人家屋企<br />\n酒店<br />\nhall都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c129efe50962cc1b6b230ad8c3f4fa5450f556","tid":298515,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以前係面向天會成日有事，打側就好d<br />\n<br />\n而家已經少左好多，冇咩事，但冇特別做d咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪無壓力了"},{"pid":"6f4c0c109a91c1fe86034ce81c8cadcf88b2f066","tid":298515,"uid":113675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:14:54.000Z","msg":"以前讀書好攰試過好多次<br />\n<br />\n通常係腦諗到野但身郁唔到<br />\n<br />\n同埋個腦好多雜聲~ 係打喊露個種雜聲再放大幾倍<br />\n<br />\n通常會強迫自己用盡力吸氣~ 如是者大啖吸多幾次就無事"},{"pid":"73b76c1bf12735da977e92e065e2f478cd1b980a","tid":298515,"uid":113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:29:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想知各位巴c經歷同埋咩原因令你有and你點解決</blockquote><br />\n前晚先發生嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人太攰/瞓得太多就有機會<br />\n我每次瞓瞓下耳嗚，全身震同聽到笑聲，就知又嚟料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1.我試過壓壓下，自己行左出客廳，見到自己老母同細妹喺度食熱浪飲檸檬茶同埋講是非。之後第二日我問返佢地，佢地好驚訝點解我會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.有一次就耳嗚，全身震。跟著就發覺自己一直向下沉，見到自己背脊。<br />\n3. 一路俾鬼壓，一路見到同聽到個女人奸笑。<br />\n4 .壓壓下，自己可以起身，但望落街見到好多「人」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我已經習慣左，仲幾享受個感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3585965f66bead7fbdd782bf873b5b604c52653","tid":298515,"uid":90615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:36:21.000Z","msg":"其實好小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上一攰訓晏覺比人嘈醒都會<br />\n試過係學校圖書館比鬼壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ab3ee8bbf05180a00d5e21288e88946d491499","tid":298515,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:44:09.000Z","msg":"試過兩次, 繼續訓算9數, 反正郁唔到"},{"pid":"30ae3c6a7b00c1aac32db6805749feab39697ade","tid":298515,"uid":65207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:46:14.000Z","msg":"我都有重要係啱啱發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/26/194517_741da34db15e37096536abe5c9032f62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F26%2F194517_741da34db15e37096536abe5c9032f62.jpg&h=aaf3935c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bdc75f3d4195738bec8915c4ea588b4a4525c8c","tid":298515,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:48:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實好小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上一攰訓晏覺比人嘈醒都會<br />\n試過係學校圖書館比鬼壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每日wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明知有 但都要訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b58102f30b736589d8d0ddb6dd465768fc67da1","tid":298515,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T12:01:07.000Z","msg":"我試過  通常係訓晏教  有一次特別啲  係坐巴士訓著俾鬼壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e7d5225fb9371a99db2ce8d99f24df544a7d1f","tid":298515,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T13:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8975797e7ff4c9652afdeac22d6879ac50175524","tid":298515,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T19:27:36.000Z","msg":"通常係瞓醒但又醒唔晒仲咪緊眼個陣會感覺到黎料<br />\n會覺得有啲頭暈，眉頭自然會自己皺埋，合實對眼 跟著就黎料 <br />\n都係開唔到眼 郁唔到 然後20秒左右就開眼郁返起身再瞓過<br />\n係得一次奇怪啲見到白光先（合埋眼個陣）然後黎料聽到火車 勁共聲 覺得張床係咁震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我覺得係自己攰得濟 諗太多野 多過有鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常鬼壓床都係連續幾日黎 或者同一日幾次<br />\n仲有例如臨瞓前諗自己可能會鬼壓床 個晚好大機會黎料<br />\n所以我覺得係自己諗太多先會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3905bce6ff3a39611343cb3322bc4f0c4458a5","tid":298515,"uid":73572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T19:46:03.000Z","msg":"細個時不時會，大過好好多<br />\n有時係出唔到聲，全身好似變左石頭。<br />\n不過慢慢發現只要係發覺比鬼責個時唔會驚，叫唔出聲就唔好叫，<br />\n又唔好反抗，好快就會訓返，醒左咩事都冇。<br />\n<br />\n但最恐怖係訓個時有野擋住個鼻嘅時候比鬼責，會呼吸困難，<br />\n隻手又唔可以拎開鼻前面嘅野，係咁叫救命但冇聲出。<br />\n次次遇到咁嘅情況都以為會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}